message.body: Hey. I just got an invite to an opening in Charlestown on Friday. If you guys want to go for an adventure I can grab the details for that. If not Ill be psyched to see you for dinner on Friday. Ariel and co. May want to join us too!
Hey Megan actually decided she's going to go home and see her Fam on Friday so no worries well hang another night!
Do you want to grab dinner then with my sister and her friends. It's really no worries... I can go to the show anytime
Lets hang altogether! I may head home too this weekend
Well find a time for all of us
